text:
Peach fair, huh... Would you like to order as much as
you can eat? You've worked hard during the recording.

Then, let's skip this one...
and have this and this...!

Alright,
now all we have to do is wait.

Here you go.
We have blended coffee and peach crepe and--...?

Huh? Three desserts came out!
Did we make a mistake?

Haha... seems like it.
If it's too much, I'll eat it--

I've been moving around a lot today,
so I feel like I can handle all three!
